Chan,is,a,forum,for,image,posting,and,discussion,Users,can,post,images,to,different,threads,separated,categorically,into,themes,like,videogames,anime,music,and,more,Users,can,reply,to,images,and,comments,with,more,images,and,comments,The,pasteboard,format,is,simple,and,does,not,require,an,account,or,login,The,chan,API,exposes,information,from,the,pasteboard,s,threads,Developers,can,use,it,to,retrieve,content,from,chan,It,is,a,RESTful,API,that,returns,JSON,encoded,data